@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xidmhs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((v2 + (v2 + 0.19 - v1 + 0.45)))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.71) / v1) / 0.36)
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.90 * v2 + 0.28)) / ((v1 + 0.51 / tmp + 0.85) + tmp))
    v1 = (wp.sin(0.63) * wp.cos(0.34))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = (wp.sin(v0) / (0.26 - tmp))
    v1 = 0.52
    data[tid] = v0
